race.comment: JAI BUBBA (2) produced a moderate run last time when seventh at this track over 520m behind Oliver Grande (30.84) in a Grade 5/6. Was a winner prior to that. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Can discover winning form. THINK POSITIVE (7) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, most recently finishing 3rd at this track over 520m. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Can feature again. TRUNKEY FRANK (4) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at Wentworth Park over 520m behind Taw Major (30.51) in a Grade 5. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Likely to be about the mark. WEST ON BURNIE (8) must be included in calculations.
